comment._content: The Sydney metropolitan detail series (Google Satellite View equivalent of late 1880s) - acms.sl.nsw.gov.au/_zoomify/2008/D00663/a1367322.html - gives a clearer understanding of the former layout of the buildings at the intersection.

comment.author: 32162360@N00
comment._content: Re the date - from the GoogleMapsStreetView above, the buildings which replaced this corner shop (Bob Janes and the blocks of units) look to be c.1930, which would make this photo late 1920s.  Also the 1920s car in Reddy Street behind.
